She gets hit with a photon blast and is thrown back against the wall.
She slowly gets up and looks at the wound in her chest an shoulder.
It was leaking mech fliud pretty heavily.  She looked at Quickstrike 
and Paralysis.  She walked over and stood between them. She fired on 
the Maximals.
